Amid the ongoing controversy surrounding Datti Baba, who is set to be unveiled as the running mate to Mr. Peter Obi, the Presidential candidate of the party for the 2023 elections, Reno Omokri, a Socio-political activist and Former presidential aid has taken to His verified Twitter to assert that the Most Foolish Thing Anyone Can Do Is To Underestimate Datti Baba.
Reno Omokri Made this statement While replying to a Twitter user Who Opined that Datti Baba is not fit To be the running mate of Peter Obi. According to the Twitter user, Peter Obi pick the wrong candidate, a person that can not Win his ward in Zaria Local Government in Kaduna.
Reno Omokri While reacting to this statement Asked the Twitter user if he knew that Datti Baba defeated the former Kaduna State Governor, Ahmed Makarfi. According to The activist, Datti Baba should not be underrated.
In His words”Are you aware he defeated former Kaduna Governor, Ahmed Makarfi? The most foolish thing anyone can do is to underestimate Datti Baba Ahmed. He brings something powerful to the ticket, and you don’t need to support Labour to see it”
The Labour party Will unveil Datti Baba as the running mate of Peter Obi on Friday. Datti Baba is an economist and the Proprietor of Baze University, Abuja, and Baba-Ahmed University Kano.
